{"tid":732940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙中線】土瓜灣站廢料建牆　盧偉國稱司空見慣：駛唔駛下下通報","createTime":"2018-07-07T10:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T12:49:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"70f24342e3656dbbff769dce0c4cc94250f0014e","tid":732940,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:51:49.000Z","msg":"【沙中線】土瓜灣站廢料建牆　盧偉國稱司空見慣：駛唔駛下下通報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/207514/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3%E7%AB%99%E5%BB%A2%E6%96%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%89%86-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%B8%E7%A9%BA%E8%A6%8B%E6%85%A3-%E9%A7%9B%E5%94%94%E9%A7%9B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F207514%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E5%259C%259F%25E7%2593%259C%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E7%2589%2586-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%258F%25B8%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2585%25A3-%25E9%25A7%259B%25E5%2594%2594%25E9%25A7%259B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1&d=Ej%2FVzRPZa7vKm05xBp8MlsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b1ee74a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/207514/%E6%B2%99%E4%B8%AD%E7%B7%9A-%E5%9C%9F%E7%93%9C%E7%81%A3%E7%AB%99%E5%BB%A2%E6%96%99%E5%BB%BA%E7%89%86-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E5%9C%8B%E7%A8%B1%E5%8F%B8%E7%A9%BA%E8%A6%8B%E6%85%A3-%E9%A7%9B%E5%94%94%E9%A7%9B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%9A%E5%A0%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會鐵路事宜小組委員會今日（6日）召開特別會議，商討土瓜灣站及會展站工程問題。對於早前有議員揭發土瓜灣內牆以建築廢料代替石屎建造，港鐵今日承認該牆有18%以建築廢料建造；立法會工程界議員盧偉國對此表示，在工程界利用建築廢料作回填屬「司空見慣」，更指出「駛唔駛下下通報，根本唔係一個問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前土瓜灣站被揭發內牆以建築廢料代替石屎建造，且未有事先通報港鐵。港鐵工程總監黃唯銘今日於會議中首次承認該牆有18%以回填物料建造，指出是「業界常見的做法」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>盧偉國：惰性廢料可作回填物料</strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會工程界議員盧偉國對此做法，解釋建築廢料分為惰性及非惰性，惰性物料可用作填海及工程回填物料，而非惰性的則不會用作回填之用，盧偉國稱土瓜灣工程利用惰性的回填物料屬司空見慣，根本不需懷疑。<span style=\"color: red;\">問及承建商於利用建築廢料建牆未有事先向港鐵通報的做法，盧偉國則表示「駛唔駛下下都通報，呢啲係標準野，好奇怪點會有人大造文章」。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於土瓜站承建商擅自削筋一事，未有事先向港鐵通報，盧偉國認為做法不恰當，惟對於承建商的解釋可以接受，亦稱純粹是「工程上技術問題，無任何違法」，他建議日後承建商應就工程事件與港鐵加強溝通。<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係用廢料起牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港鐵管唔掂仲要搵人9 up 辯護<br />\n整臭曬工程界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17644b446c14954abd237f7742e978df66bfd22","tid":732940,"uid":35070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:52:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恭喜香港成功與強國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"f1589eb3b47e9d1dec5a5e80b6cd7dbc2453dfde","tid":732940,"uid":1082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"人地明明話啲廢料用黎&ldquo;壓倉&rdquo;， 又比你班on 9 踢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1493b1640f052f3e61259632c13248733355f305","tid":732940,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ec6037ac6541110b7021957e3410b3fbdc8086","tid":732940,"uid":189745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:47:54.000Z","msg":"你話私人樓我未做過唔知<br />\n政府野/地鐵夠膽咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時落石屎前一個膠樽蓋都要你拎走"},{"pid":"eceefec1ff73c485db620665f88508b44b1999c9","tid":732940,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"唔係有分主唔主力牆咩?<br />\n唔係主力通常都係求其<br />\n之前咪有單用發泡膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}